        <num>CC 800</num>
        <heading>800.  Preservation of the thing</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 800.  Preservation of the thing
A co-owner may without the concurrence of any other co-owner take necessary steps for the preservation of the thing that is held in indivision.</p>
        </content>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
          <p>Source: https://www.legis.la.gov/legis/Law.aspx?d=110996</p>
